{
  "stem": "7904.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, like I mentioned before, we went to [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Shiatin. ?] This was a little town, the border of Romania and Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "On the other side was Czernowitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was our-- we thought that's going to be our destination, to-- to cross over to Czernowitz, and from Czernowitz, to go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That time it was Palestine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But [LAUGHS]-- but we got caught from Jewish militia, from the Jewish boys, communists.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They became militia right away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they told us, hey, you want to go to Palestine?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You have to-- you have to stay here, to build a communist-- a communist country.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they put us in jail.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At that time, I-- like I-- I told you yesterday, I had a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they said, the capitalist, if they find a lot of money, they will send us to Siberia, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I took the money and I split on three-- three ways.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "After they-- and present, they sent us back to Lemberg.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The money I never saw again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] The [INAUDIBLE]-- I split with the other two guys.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I never saw again.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But coming back to Lemberg, I met a fellow from my town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He knew the family.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He knew me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was surprised that I am here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, listen, they think-- they think that you got-- you got killed in you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because your father came home without you, and they put up already candles after me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I told myself, I have to go home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have to go home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that time, there was a time when the border was open between Russia and Germany.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Polish-- Polish territory, where the Russian took over, and the Germany-- and Polish, where the German took over.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
